'''二苯基膦基锂'''是一种化合物，化学式为(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PLi，它是对空气敏感的固体，可用于制备其它含二苯基膦基团的化合物。其乙醚配合物是红色的。
[[File:DOXDUP.png|thumb]]|journal=Inorg. Chem.|year=1986|volume=25|pages=1243–1247|doi=10.1021/ic00228a034}}</ref>]]

==合成==
二苯基膦基锂可由[[二苯基氯化膦|二苯基氯化膦]]、<ref>{{cite journal
|journal=Inorganic Syntheses
|title=Diphenyl(trimethylsilyl)phosphine and Dimethyl(trimethylsilyl)‐phosphine
|authors=R. Goldsberry  Kim Cohn
|year=1972|volume=13|pages=26-32
|doi=10.1002/9780470132449.ch7}}</ref>[[三苯基膦|三苯基膦]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Syntheses|title=Lithium Diphenylphosphide and Diphenyl(Trimethylsilyl)Phosphine|authors=George W. Luther, III, Gordon Beyerle|year=1977|volume=17|pages=186-188|doi=10.1002/9780470132487.ch51}}</ref><ref name=Bianco>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Syntheses|title=Diphenylphosphine |authors=V. D. Bianco, S. Doronzo|year=1976|volume=16|pages=161-188|doi=10.1002/9780470132470.ch43}}</ref>或[[四苯基二膦|四苯基二膦]]被金属钠还原得到：
:(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PCl  +  2 Li   →  (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PLi  +  LiCl
:(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>3</sub>P  +  2 Li   →  (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PLi  +  LiC<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>
:(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>4</sub>P<sub>2</sub>  +  2 Li   →  2 (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PLi
它也可由[[二苯基膦|二苯基膦]]脱氢得到。

==反应==
二苯基膦基锂可以在水中[[水解|水解]]，生成二苯基膦：<ref name=Bianco/>
:(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PLi  +  H<sub>2</sub>O   →   (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PH  +  LiOH

它和卤代烃反应，生成叔膦：<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Syntheses|title=''Cis''‐2‐Diphenylarsinovinyldiphenylphosphine and 2‐Diphenylarsinoethyldiphenylphosphine|authors=W. Levason, C. A. Mcauliffe |year=1976|volume=16|pages=188-192|doi=10.1002/9780470132470.ch50 }}</ref>
:(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PLi  +  RX   →   (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PR  +  LiX
例如，它和[[1,6-二氯己烷|1,6-二氯己烷]]在[[四氢呋喃|四氢呋喃]]中反应，可以得到1,6-双(二苯基膦基)己烷。<ref>Cao, Guangxiu; Ma, Huailing; Li, Guanliang; Li, Jiqin. Study on synthesis of 1,​6-​bis(diphenylphosphinel)​hexane. ''Huaxue Yanjiu Yu Yingyong'', 2006. 18 (12): 1464-1468.</ref>

它可用作甲基[[季铵盐|季铵盐]]的脱甲基试剂。<ref>Plenat, Francoise; Cahyono, Bambang; Cristau, Henri-Jean. Lithium diphenylphosphide: a new demethylation reagent for methylammonium salts. ''Comptes Rendus de l'Academie des Sciences, Serie IIb: Mecanique,Physique, Chimie, Astronomie'', 1995. 320 (10): 539-543. ISSN: 1251-8069.</ref>它和金属卤化物（或有机金属卤化物<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Alcalde|first1=Maria Isabel|last2=de la Mata|first2=Javier|last3=Gómez|first3=Manuel|last4=Royo|first4=pascual|last5=Sánchez|first5=Fernando|title=Half-sandwich isocyanide, phosphine, methyl and phosphanido pentamethylcyclopentadienylniobium (V) complexes|journal=Journal of Organometallic Chemistry|volume=492|issue=2|year=1995|pages=151–155|issn=0022328X|doi=10.1016/0022-328X(94)05289-N}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Cano|first1=Ana|last2=Cuenca|first2=Tomás|last3=Galakhov|first3=Mikhail|last4=Rodríguez|first4=Gema M.|last5=Royo|first5=Pascual|last6=Cardin|first6=Christine J.|last7=Convery|first7=Maire A.|title=Fulvalene titanium and zirconium complexes: synthesis and NMR study of phosphanido-, alkyl-, and alkynyl-derivatives. X-ray crystal structures of [{Ti(η5−C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)(μ−PPH<sub>2</sub>)}<sub>2</sub>{μ−(η5−C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>−η5−C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>)}] and [{Zr(η5−C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)(μ−C≡CSiMe<sub>3</sub>)}<sub>2</sub>{μ−(η5−C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>−η5−C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>)}]|journal=Journal of Organometallic Chemistry|volume=493|issue=1-2|year=1995|pages=17–25|issn=0022328X|doi=10.1016/0022-328X(94)05288-M}}</ref>）反应，生成过渡金属{{le|膦配合物|Transition metal phosphido complexes}}。<ref>Issleib, Kurt; Froehlich, Hans Otto. Alkali metal-​phosphorus compounds and their reactive behavior. XIII. Preparation and properties of zinc and cuprous diphenylphosphide. ''Chemische Berichte'', 1962. 95: 375-380. ISSN: 0009-2940.</ref>

